
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Flexproof — Recruitment as a Service</title>
<meta name="description" content="Flexproof regelt jouw volledige recruitmentproces als vast maandabonnement. Transparant, schaalbaar en volledig remote. Geen CV-schuivers, geen torenhoge fees.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bricolage+Grotesque:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --ink:#0B0F1A;
  --surface:#F5F3EE;
  --card:#FFFFFF;
  --accent:#00C896;
  --accent-dark:#009970;
  --muted:#6B7280;
  --border:#E5E2DC;
  --red:#E24B4A;
  --hf:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;
  --bf:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--surface);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--bf);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6}

/* NAV */
nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(245,243,238,0.93);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 40px;height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--hf);font-weight:800;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.5px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink)}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--accent)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{text-decoration:none;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}
.nav-cta{background:var(--ink)!important;color:#fff!important;padding:10px 22px;border-radius:100px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600!important;transition:background 0.2s!important}
.nav-cta:hover{background:#1d2740!important}

/* HERO */
.hero{padding:96px 40px 72px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#E8FBF5;color:#00875F;border:1px solid #B3EDD8;border-radius:100px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:28px}
.pulse{width:7px;height:7px;background:#00C896;border-radius:50%;animation:pulse 2s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:0.5;transform:scale(0.85)}}
h1{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,68px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-2px;max-width:780px;margin-bottom:22px}
h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--accent)}
.hero-sub{font-size:18px;color:var(--muted);max-width:520px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:36px;font-weight:300}
.btn-row{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:56px}
.btn-primary{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;transition:all 0.2s}
.btn-primary:hover{background:#1d2740;transform:translateY(-1px)}
.btn-secondary{color:var(--ink);padding:14px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--border);transition:all 0.2s}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:#999}
.hero-stats{display:flex;gap:48px;padding-top:40px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap}
.stat-num{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:38px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.5px;line-height:1}
.stat-num span{color:var(--accent)}
.stat-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px}

/* SECTIONS */
.section{padding:80px 40px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto}
.section-tag{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:14px}
.section-title{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,42px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1px;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:14px}
.section-title em{font-style:normal;color:var(--accent)}
.section-sub{font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);max-width:480px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:300}

/* DARK BAND */
.dark-band{background:var(--ink);padding:56px 40px}
.dark-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.dark-title{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,34px);font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-0.5px;line-height:1.2}
.dark-title em{font-style:normal;color:var(--accent)}
.tag-row{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:14px}
.chip{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-radius:100px;padding:5px 14px;font-size:13px}

/* PAIN */
.pain-block{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:4px solid var(--red);border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;padding:28px 32px;margin-bottom:32px}
.pain-title{font-family:var(--hf);font-weight:800;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:16px}
.pain-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.pain-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
.pain-dot{width:6px;height:6px;background:var(--red);border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:8px}

/* VS */
.vs-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto 1fr;gap:16px;align-items:start;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:28px;margin-bottom:28px}
.vs-col-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px}
.vs-col-title.bad{color:var(--red)}
.vs-col-title.good{color:var(--accent)}
.vs-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.45;margin-bottom:10px}
.ci{flex-shrink:0;width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;margin-top:2px}
.ci.bad{background:#FEE2E2;color:var(--red)}
.ci.good{background:#E8FBF5;color:var(--accent-dark)}
.vs-mid{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:var(--border);text-align:center;padding-top:32px}

/* BENEFITS */
.benefits-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:40px}
.b-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:24px;transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s}
.b-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 10px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.07)}
.b-card.dark{background:var(--ink);border-color:var(--ink)}
.b-icon{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:12px;display:block}
.b-title{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.3px;margin-bottom:6px}
.b-card.dark .b-title{color:#fff}
.b-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.b-card.dark .b-desc{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)}

/* STEPS */
.steps-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:40px}
.step{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:24px}
.step-n{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:42px;font-weight:800;color:var(--border);letter-spacing:-2px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:14px}
.step-t{font-family:var(--hf);font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:6px}
.step-d{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}

/* PRICING */
.pricing-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:40px}
.p-card{background:var(--card);border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:22px;padding:32px;position:relative;transition:all 0.2s}
.p-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
.p-card.featured{border-color:var(--accent);border-width:2px}
.feat-badge{position:absolute;top:-12px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--accent);color:var(--ink);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:100px;white-space:nowrap}
.p-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px}
.p-price{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:44px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.5px;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px}
.p-price small{font-size:15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0;color:var(--muted)}
.p-fee-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#E8FBF5;color:#009970;border-radius:100px;padding:4px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;margin:10px 0 16px}
.p-divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:16px 0}
.p-features{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;margin-bottom:24px}
.p-features li{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px}
.fc{color:var(--accent);font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.p-btn{display:block;text-align:center;padding:13px;border-radius:100px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;border:none;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s}
.p-btn-dark{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}
.p-btn-dark:hover{background:#1d2740}
.p-btn-green{background:var(--accent);color:var(--ink)}
.p-btn-green:hover{background:var(--accent-dark)}
.p-btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border:1.5px solid var(--border)}
.p-btn-outline:hover{border-color:#999}
.p-note{background:#F8F7F4;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-top:20px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.p-note strong{color:var(--ink)}

/* CALCULATOR */
.calc-box{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:32px;margin-top:40px}
.calc-title{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin-bottom:6px}
.calc-sub{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:24px}
.calc-controls{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-bottom:24px}
.c-field label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:8px}
.c-field input[type=range]{width:100%;accent-color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:6px}
.c-field select{width:100%;padding:9px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-family:var(--bf);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);background:var(--surface);outline:none}
.c-val{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.5px}
.results-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px}
.r-box{background:var(--surface);border-radius:12px;padding:16px}
.r-box.win{background:var(--ink)}
.r-lbl{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:6px}
.r-box.win .r-lbl{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}
.r-num{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.5px;line-height:1;color:var(--ink)}
.r-box.win .r-num{color:var(--accent)}
.r-detail{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}
.r-box.win .r-detail{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)}
.breakdown{background:var(--surface);border-radius:12px;padding:16px}
.b-title-s{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px}
.b-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:13px}
.b-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;padding-top:10px;font-weight:600}
.b-name{color:var(--ink)}
.col-red{color:var(--red)}
.col-green{color:var(--accent-dark)}
.col-muted{color:var(--muted)}

/* STATS */
.stats-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:32px}
.stat-box{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center}
.stat-big{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:34px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1px;color:var(--accent);line-height:1}
.stat-lbl{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.4}

/* CTA */
.cta-section{background:var(--ink);border-radius:28px;padding:64px 56px;text-align:center;margin:0 40px 60px}
.cta-section h2{font-family:var(--hf);font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,44px);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:#fff;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:14px}
.cta-section h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--accent)}
.cta-section p{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:32px}
.cta-btns{display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn-white{background:#fff;color:var(--ink);padding:14px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s}
.btn-white:hover{background:#eee}
.btn-ghost{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);padding:14px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);transition:all 0.2s}
.btn-ghost:hover{color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)}

/* FORM */
.contact-form{background:var(--card);border-radius:20px;padding:36px;margin-top:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);text-align:left}
.form-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
.form-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.form-group.full{grid-column:1/-1}
.form-group label{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.8px;color:var(--muted)}
.form-group input,.form-group select,.form-group textarea{padding:12px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-family:var(--bf);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);background:var(--surface);outline:none;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.form-group input:focus,.form-group select:focus,.form-group textarea:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.form-group textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:120px}
.form-submit{background:var(--accent);color:var(--ink);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:100px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:var(--bf)}
.form-submit:hover{background:var(--accent-dark);color:#fff}
.form-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:12px}
/* FOOTER */
.footer{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.footer-logo{font-family:var(--hf);font-weight:800;font-size:18px}
.footer-logo span{color:var(--accent)}
.footer-copy{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Flex<span>proof</span></a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#voordelen">Voordelen</a>
    <a href="#hoe">Hoe het werkt</a>
    <a href="#prijzen">Prijzen</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Kennismaking plannen</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge"><span class="pulse"></span>Remote-first recruitment — geen gedoe, wel resultaat</div>
  <h1>Werving uit handen.<br><em>Talent</em> in huis.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Flexproof regelt jouw volledige recruitmentproces als vast maandabonnement. Transparant, schaalbaar en tot 60% goedkoper dan een traditioneel bureau.</p>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="#prijzen" class="btn-primary">Bekijk pakketten →</a>
    <a href="#voordelen" class="btn-secondary">Waarom RaaS?</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">14<span>d</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Gemiddelde time-to-candidate</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">60<span>%</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Goedkoper bij 4+ hires/jaar</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">0</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Verborgen kosten</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="stat-num">100<span>%</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">Remote proces mogelijk</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DARK BAND -->
<div class="dark-band">
  <div class="dark-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="dark-title">Voor <em>start- en scale-ups</em><br>die snel willen groeien.</div>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">Sales professionals</span>
        <span class="chip">IT & Tech</span>
        <span class="chip">Tijdelijke versterking</span>
        <span class="chip">Noord-Brabant & remote</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-white" style="background:#fff;color:var(--ink);padding:14px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap">Plan een kennismaking</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- VOORDELEN -->
<div class="section" id="voordelen">
  <div class="section-tag">Waarom RaaS</div>
  <div class="section-title">Klaar met CV-schuivers<br>en <em>hoge fees?</em></div>
  <p class="section-sub">Traditionele bureaus sturen bulk, vragen torenhoge fees en verdwijnen zodra de factuur betaald is. Flexproof werkt anders.</p>

  <div style="margin-top:32px">
    <div class="pain-block">
      <div class="pain-title">Herken jij dit?</div>
      <div class="pain-list">
        <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-dot"></span>Je ontvangt een stapel cv's waarvan 80% niet eens aan het profiel voldoet</div>
        <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-dot"></span>Bij een aanname betaal je €8.000–€15.000 per hire, ongeacht hoe lang diegene blijft</div>
        <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-dot"></span>Het bureau kent je bedrijf nauwelijks en pitcht dezelfde kandidaten bij meerdere klanten tegelijk</div>
        <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-dot"></span>Geen inzicht in het proces — je wacht maar af en hoopt op een match</div>
        <div class="pain-item"><span class="pain-dot"></span>Na plaatsing hoor je nooit meer iets — geen evaluatie, geen opvolging</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vs-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="vs-col-title bad">Traditioneel bureau</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci bad">✕</span>22,5% fee per hire — geen plafond</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci bad">✕</span>Bulk cv's zonder diepgang</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci bad">✕</span>Kandidaat op naam van bureau</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci bad">✕</span>Geen procesregie of transparantie</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci bad">✕</span>Transactioneel — weg na plaatsing</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci bad">✕</span>Geen employer branding voordeel</div>
      </div>
      <div class="vs-mid">vs</div>
      <div>
        <div class="vs-col-title good">Flexproof RaaS</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci good">✓</span>Vast bedrag + lage succesfee (8–12%)</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci good">✓</span>Alleen gekwalificeerde shortlist</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci good">✓</span>Werving onder jouw naam en merk</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci good">✓</span>Wekelijkse updates en volledige inzage</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci good">✓</span>Langdurig partnerschap, maandelijks opzegbaar</div>
        <div class="vs-item"><span class="ci good">✓</span>Jouw employer brand wordt sterker</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="benefits-grid">
    <div class="b-card"><span class="b-icon">🎯</span><div class="b-title">Kwaliteit boven kwantiteit</div><div class="b-desc">Geen stapels cv's maar een scherpe shortlist van 3–5 echt passende kandidaten. Jij praat alleen met mensen die er toe doen.</div></div>
    <div class="b-card"><span class="b-icon">🏷️</span><div class="b-title">Werving onder jouw naam</div><div class="b-desc">Vacatures gaan de markt op met jouw bedrijfsnaam. Dat versterkt je employer brand — niet dat van een bureau.</div></div>
    <div class="b-card"><span class="b-icon">📊</span><div class="b-title">Volledig inzicht en regie</div><div class="b-desc">Je weet altijd waar het proces staat. Wekelijkse updates, maandelijkse rapportage en een vast aanspreekpunt.</div></div>
